Great questions

The motivation case from many things, among them this tweet: https://twitter.com/leahculver/status/1269109776983547904?s=21
One can find more about this topic here: https://tools.ietf.org/id/draft-knodel-terminology-00.html

I consider it a “bug”, because I don’t think it is a new feature. Since we are just modifying private properties and internal names, this could be considered a CS fix.

