@phansys I am not sure what you concern is here. are you concerned that humanities wrong doing will leave no word not attached to a traumatic experience? if that is your argument, then don’t worry, human language is constantly evolving, so new words will be created.

if your concern is about clarity, then I would wager that blocklist is clearer to the novice than blacklist.

that being said, I personally would prefer using the term “denylist”.

