by phansys at 2020-06-07T18:42:09Z

>@phansys I am not sure what you concern is here. are you concerned that humanities wrong doing will leave no word not attached to a traumatic experience?

My main concern is near your first statement and the effort it demand versus the gain we get. I don't think using the term "black" or "white", "left" or "right" should be associated to scopes or aspects that aren't related to what we are doing here.
IMHO, adding more words to the "blocklist" of forbidden terms brings a bad DX.
Personally, I don't consider as evolution the fact to convalidate any of the mentioned terms such something wrong, bad, despective, etc.

